---
title: AI Flow — Workflow State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> backlog

    backlog --> planning : assign

    planning --> plan_approval : plan ready
    plan_approval --> test_planning : approved
    plan_approval --> planning : revise

    test_planning --> test_plan_approval : test plan ready
    test_plan_approval --> test_implementation : approved
    test_plan_approval --> test_planning : revise

    test_implementation --> test_approval : tests written
    test_approval --> implementation : approved
    test_approval --> test_implementation : revise

    implementation --> implementation_approval : code ready
    implementation_approval --> completed : approved
    implementation_approval --> implementation : revise

    completed --> [*]

    note right of planning
        Claude generates
        implementation plan
    end note

    note right of plan_approval
        Human reviews via
        GitHub / Slack signal
    end note
